392
00:26:38.965 --> 00:26:40.199
Hey.

393
00:26:40.299 --> 00:26:41.300
We ain't done here.

394
00:26:41.400 --> 00:26:43.502
I am.
[chuffs]

395
00:26:43.636 --> 00:26:45.304
