That was a close call.

399
00:27:03.990 --> 00:27:05.892
[both laugh]

400
00:27:08.460 --> 00:27:09.561
Where's Ms. Jackson?

401
00:27:09.662 --> 00:27:10.697
- We got this.
- Ooh. there she is.

402
00:27:10.830 --> 00:27:12.197
- Okay...
- Mm.

403
00:27:12.198 --> 00:27:14.366
- [laughs]
- Okay. Go. go.

404
00:27:14.500 --> 00:27:16.068
[chuckles]

405
00:27:18.370 --> 00:27:20.673
♪ slow. dramatic music ♪

406
00:27:20.807 --> 00:27:22.942
[cattle lowing]

407
00:27:23.042 --> 00:27:24.476
[cowboy chuffing]

408
00:27:24.576 --> 00:27:26.545
[cowboy 2]
<i>Ganado San Manuel.</i>

409
00:27:26.645 --> 00:27:28.580
[cowboy 3]
<i>A huevo. viejo.</i>

410
00:27:29.348 --> 00:27:31.583
[cowboy chuffing]

411
00:27:36.388 --> 00:27:38.190
[cowboy whistles]

412
00:27:38.290 --> 00:27:41.360
[cowboys hollering]

413
00:28:08.888 --> 00:28:11.423
[hollering continues]

414
00:28:22.201 --> 00:28:23.601
Fence done?

415
00:28:23.602 --> 00:28:24.904
Yeah. got it.

416
00:28:25.004 --> 00:28:26.572
The cattle ain't as fleshy
as Rip likes.

417
00:28:26.705 --> 00:28:28.640
We're gonna run 'em across
the scales. worm 'em again.

418
00:28:30.843 --> 00:28:31.910
[cattle bellowing]

419
00:28:31.911 --> 00:28:33.611
Fuck. <i>Pendejo.</i>

420
00:28:33.612 --> 00:28:35.481
[clicks tongue]

421
00:28:39.085 --> 00:28:40.452
Rookie mistake.

422
00:28:41.187 --> 00:28:43.121
Triple-check every fucking gate.

423
00:28:43.122 --> 00:28:45.657
- Frank. Tommy. grab that one.
- I got it. I got it.

424
00:28:54.466 --> 00:28:55.667
Rip!

425
00:28:55.768 --> 00:28:57.837
♪ tense. suspenseful music ♪

426
00:28:57.937 --> 00:28:59.105
Shit.

427
00:28:59.205 --> 00:29:00.739
[groans]

428
00:29:01.540 --> 00:29:02.808
- Hey. you okay?
- [grunts]

429
00:29:02.809 --> 00:29:04.977
[strains]
Yeah. I'm-I'm fine.

430
00:29:05.978 --> 00:29:07.814
Hey. your horse ain't going
nowhere. Let me get you checked.

431
00:29:07.947 --> 00:29:09.448
I said I'm fucking fine. Azul.

432
00:29:09.548 --> 00:29:11.617
Hey! Don't you yell at him.

433
00:29:13.119 --> 00:29:14.620
Get on your horse.

434
00:29:17.389 --> 00:29:18.825
[Carter grunts]

435
00:29:19.625 --> 00:29:21.260
Fuck this shit.

436
00:29:29.735 --> 00:29:31.971
Go back to work. Let's go.

437
00:29:41.147 --> 00:29:45.617
Just gonna straighten up a sec
and make the bed for you.

438
00:29:45.717 --> 00:29:47.820
Just make yourself comfortable.

439
00:29:47.954 --> 00:29:50.222
[chuckling]
Yeah. don't mind me.

440
00:29:51.390 --> 00:29:53.059
I can make you some...

441
00:29:53.159 --> 00:29:55.327
chamomile tea
if you'd like. but...

442
00:29:55.427 --> 00:29:59.631
don't go asking me
for my. for my whiskey.

443
00:30:01.100 --> 00:30:03.335
♪ gentle music ♪

444
00:30:14.280 --> 00:30:16.415
Sleep?

445
00:30:20.219 --> 00:30:22.421
