518
00:36:23.949 --> 00:36:25.451
Issue a warrant.

519
00:36:26.652 --> 00:36:28.554
And where's Wes's body?

520
00:36:28.687 --> 00:36:30.422
I don't know.

521
00:36:30.522 --> 00:36:32.658
- You don't know.
- I-I'm working on it.

522
00:36:32.758 --> 00:36:34.926
